item.title: CVE-2020-8966|2024-08-04T10:19:19.521Z -- tiki-wiki%20groupware -- tiki-wiki%20cms
item.description: There is an Improper Neutralization of Script-Related HTML Tags in a Web Page (Basic XSS) vulnerability in php webpages of Tiki-Wiki Groupware. Tiki-Wiki CMS all versions through 20.0 allows malicious users to cause the injection of malicious code fragments (scripts) into a legitimate web page.
